GLM

Run a simple model for Priciple Conponent

reg <- glm(CASE_STATUS ~ ., data = H1B_Train)
X <- model.matrix(reg)
pc <- stats::prcomp(X)
pc
100 * (pc$sdev/sum(pc$sdev)) |>
    round(3)
## the output is too long so the r chuck set it as not
## showing output
summary(pc)

PC Plot

screeplot(pc)

pc$rotation[, 1] |>
    round(3)
pc_s <- prcomp(X[, -1])
pc_s
summary(pc_s)
screeplot(pc_s)

mean((yHat_pls - H1B_Test$CASE_STATUS)^2)
